\"Kayla Harrison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Harrison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Harrison\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2462}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Inlast week's column, I began to detail what she did to overcome years of sexual abuse by her trusted family-friend and coach.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Inlast week's column\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2504}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 2558, \"to\": 2570}, {\"ngram\": \"her trusted family-friend\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2599}, {\"ngram\": \"coach\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though I encourage youread these stepsin her own words, her first three steps were: 1) Do not let being a victim define or paralyze you; rather, use it as a catalyst and fuel for victory; 2) Surround yourself with people who will push - and sometimes even pull - you toward your goals; and 3) Make a commitment to keep stepping forward, however small the baby steps or reeling the relapses; mark your progress; celebrate the small victories and the major milestones.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 3078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her own words\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"her first three steps\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2689}, {\"ngram\": \"a victim define\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2731}, {\"ngram\": \"a catalyst\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2777}, {\"ngram\": \"fuel\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2798}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2832}, {\"ngram\": \"your goals\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2896}, {\"ngram\": \"a commitment\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"the relapses\", \"from\": 2989, \"to\": 3001}, {\"ngram\": \"your progress\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3021}, {\"ngram\": \"the small victories\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3052}, {\"ngram\": \"the major milestones\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are a three more inspiring lessons Kayla's life and actions teach us: 4.\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3158, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3120, \"end\": 3125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5383012633043245e-37, \"text\": \"Kayla\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a three more inspiring lessons\", \"from\": 3089, \"to\": 3119}, {\"ngram\": \"actions\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3151, \"to\": 3153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Constantly visualize your recovery, goals, and a better tomorrow.\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3224, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your recovery\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"goals\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"a better tomorrow\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3223}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she sat by her coaches, Jimmy Pedro and Jimmy Sr., Kayla testified: \\\"We practice a lot of visualization, and every night before I go to sleep I would walk through my day and I would picture my Olympic journey and I would picture every moment of it.\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jimmy Pedro\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Pedro\"}, {\"begin\": 3280, \"end\": 3285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kayla_Brady\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5383012633043245e-37, \"text